<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlfjr sẖq wlạḥ ẓhr lh ṣbạḥ(2)
 lmạ ạ̉tyt lyswʿ ẓlạmy wly̱ wrạḥ
 1-(snyn wwrạhạ snyn wạ̉yạm btjyb ạ̉yạm
 wlyạly bṭwlhạ ạ̉nyn msẖḥwnh bạlạ̉whạm) (2)
 wạlwhm dạ bḥrh kbyr wʿmyq wmạlhsẖ qrạr(2)
 wạnạ ʿsẖt fy mwjh ạsyr ylṭmny lyl wnhạr(2)
 lḥd mạ jạny yswʿ njạty wqạl ly ạrtạḥ
 2-(lyh qạʿd lyh ḥyrạn wạlfkr sẖryd tʿbạn
 wsmạk mlyạnh gẖywm wlạ sẖmsk ywm btbạn) (2)
 mstny ạ̉yh mạ tqwm wtʿạl lly fdạk(2)</lyrics>
<title>ạlfjr sẖq wlạḥ</title>
<hymn_number>10215</hymn_number>
</song>